      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to prevent certain individuals purportedly appointed to the National Labor Relations Board from receiving salaries, and to prevent an unconstitutional quorum of the Board from taking agency actions, until there is a final decision in pending lawsuits regarding the constitutionality of certain alleged recess appointments.</title>
      </item>
